
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant Conv as Conversation Service
    participant ConvDB as Conversation DB
    participant RabbitMQ as RabbitMQ Broker
    participant Chatbot as Chatbot Service
    participant ChatbotDB as Chatbot DB
    participant R2 as R2 Object Storage

    User->>+Conv: POST /code-conversation-service/shares/:id/revoke
    Conv->>+ConvDB: UPDATE Share (isActive=false) & INSERT Outbox (ShareRevokedEvent)
    ConvDB-->>-Conv: Commit Transaction (Atomic)
    Conv-->>-User: HTTP 200 OK (Xác nhận thu hồi thành công)

    Note over Conv, RabbitMQ: Cron job OutboxRelay quét DB định kỳ gửi event
    Conv->>+ConvDB: SELECT PENDING OutboxEvents
    ConvDB-->>-Conv: Danh sách events
    Conv->>+RabbitMQ: Publish 'ShareRevokedEvent' (Queue: share_revoked)
    RabbitMQ-->>-Conv: Ack
    Conv->>+ConvDB: UPDATE Outbox status='DONE'
    ConvDB-->>-Conv: OK

    RabbitMQ-->>+Chatbot: Consume 'ShareRevokedEvent'
    Chatbot->>+R2: Yêu cầu xóa file JSONL khỏi R2 (delete_file)
    R2-->>-Chatbot: OK (Đã xóa file)

    Chatbot->>+ChatbotDB: UPDATE Share (is_revoked=True, version=version)
    ChatbotDB-->>-Chatbot: OK
    Chatbot-->>-RabbitMQ: Acknowledge (Hoàn thành)
